data.description:
Amazing Value!  It's not often that you find a new home with 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms price under $400,000.  This turn-key property has so much to offer.  Popular single-level spacious floor plan providing lots of room for everyone!  Beautiful kitchen and living room perfect for entertaining!  

The backyard has low-maintenance landscape so you can enjoy your time outside.  Turf, pavers, a fire pit, and Tiki bar!  Did I mention you have no backyard neighbors, you back to an open area that will allow you to enjoy desert views and Arizona sunsets!  Don't miss this one!
